metadata.name: CROWD
metadata.description:
There are people around me, too many of them. They are so fast, so real. I can't really see them, don't even know who they are. I hear them so loud, but the words have no meaning. Maybe they do, but I can't understand. I don't even try to talk anymore. I'm definitely invisible. I know that I'm not one of them but they are too many. And it's hard to be just me. 

This collection is a 3D animation series, focuses on the loneliest moments. 

1300 x 1700 px
